  "name": "Update Menu HUD",
  "symbol": "script_update_menu_hud",
  "description": "Deprecated for the scene-based menu until values can render without a full-screen overlay. Font mapping is retained for later use: GBS Mono HUD Petal=127, Bone=141, empty box=142, Talon=143, Nectar=156.",
